                Genio <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>I <expan><abbr>adi</abbr><ex>utricis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>idelis</ex></expan> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/> <lb n="3"/>sc<expan><ex>h</ex><abbr>olae</abbr></expan> ||(centurionum) ob ho<lb break="no" n="4"/>norem <expan><abbr>d<am>d</am></abbr><ex>ominorum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>ostrorum</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Silv<supplied reason="lost">i</supplied>nius <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Lu<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">ci</supplied>us <lb n="7"/>ex optione <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> II <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustae</ex></expan> <lb n="9"/><expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>onum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>edit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Mittelteil eines Altars oder einer Basis; Oberfläche sehr stark verwittert; kreisförmige Eintiefung auf der Oberseite; in der Mitte des Inschriftfeldes ein quadratisches Loch; Spuren roter Farbe. Das Inschriftfeld ist stark verwittert.</p>
            </div>
